=== 1.3.2 2014-08-11

* Added SSL toggle to all API calls.

=== 1.3.0 2014-07-30

*** CAUTION: THIS VERSION HAS UPDATED METHODS THAT MAKE PREVIOUS FUNCTION CALLS OBSOLETE ***
* Added timeline support.
* Added createCollection method.
* Updated createCollectionMeta() to take in optional param in an array.
* Added support for making calls using the WP client.
* Updated checksum formula.
* Refactored core objects.
* Updated majority of API calls to use SSL.

=== 1.2.0 2014-06-12

* Added personalized stream API support.
* Reorganized the library structure for consistency between different languages.

=== 1.1.8 2014-06-11

* Used IDNA class to encode UTF-8 characters so that dependency on ext-intl is no longer required.

=== 1.1.7 2014-06-10

* Copied JWT over so that minimum-stability-dev is not required.

=== 1.1.5 2014-05-13

* Bug fix for setUserSyncUrl.

=== 1.1.4 2014-05-07

* Added rating, counting as acceptable types.
* Removed stream_type.

=== 1.1.3 2014-04-23

* Renaming stream to type.
* Added checks to make sure that type is of a recognized type.
* Added legacy stream_type support.

=== 1.1.2 2014-04-10

* Fixed validateLivefyreToken.
* Adjusted collectionMetaToken to allow IDNs.

=== 1.1.1 2014-04-08

* Moved build checksum into its own method.

=== 1.0.0 2014-04-07

* Initial commit.